Package org.eclipse.papyrus.arrowhead.profile.arrowheadsysmlprofile

Interface CertificateCreationForm

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
CertificateCreationFormImpl
public interface CertificateCreationForm extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
A representation of the model object 'Certificate Creation Form'.

The following features are supported:

  • Base Class
  • Commom Name
  • Key Algorithm
  • Key Format
  • Privat Key
  • Public Key
